Ctrl + Enter: Run the current cell
Shift + Enter: Run the current cell and move to the next cell
Alt + Enter: Run the current cell and insert a new cell below
Ctrl + S: Save the notebook
Ctrl + M A: Insert a new cell above the current cell
Ctrl + M B: Insert a new cell below the current cell
Ctrl + M D: Delete the current cell
Ctrl + M M: Change the current cell to markdown mode
Ctrl + M Y: Change the current cell to code mode
Ctrl + /: Comment/uncomment the current line or selected lines
